00:09:17.912 --> 00:09:19.747
I remembered something.

00:09:19.830 --> 00:09:20.915
CLOSED FOR BUSINESS
PLEASE TAKE FREELY - FLOWER SAKURAYA

00:09:21.832 --> 00:09:25.586
The reason why I'm able to bloom flowers.

00:09:28.339 --> 00:09:30.591
A child's eyes are beautiful, right?

00:09:31.634 --> 00:09:34.845
Untouched by anything dirty.

00:09:35.471 --> 00:09:38.140
