I'm an Esper who might kill people.

00:10:06.419 --> 00:10:08.129
That's what I am.

00:10:11.716 --> 00:10:13.968
I scared Shion.

00:10:14.802 --> 00:10:16.178
I made him hate me.

00:10:20.015 --> 00:10:21.600
Who needs

00:10:24.019 --> 00:10:25.479
someone like that

00:10:28.315 --> 00:10:29.442
as a father?

00:10:37.199 --> 00:10:39.493
I lectured Shion.

00:10:39.577 --> 00:10:42.288
I told him to stop using his esper powers,
and to stop messing around.

00:10:43.956 --> 00:10:45.207
When I told him

00:10:45.291 --> 00:10:48.169
"I" disappeared again because of him,

00:10:48.252 --> 00:10:50.379
he was totally crushed.

00:10:51.797 --> 00:10:53.716
I regret saying too much.

00:10:54.967 --> 00:10:56.385
It's a good lesson for a kid, right?

00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:00.931
"I" is still gone?

00:11:03.768 --> 00:11:05.144
Am I really going to die?

00:11:08.314 --> 00:11:09.607
You'll be fine.

00:11:10.649 --> 00:11:11.901
You lived

00:11:11.984 --> 00:11:14.612
until 2055 once already.

00:11:15.654 --> 00:11:17.156
You're not dying that easily.

00:11:19.700 --> 00:11:24.079
This world has something like inertia.

00:11:26.499 --> 00:11:29.919
I know about inertia,
but why does that matter now?

00:11:30.628 --> 00:11:33.422
Altering history always causes pushback.

00:11:34.715 --> 00:11:36.342
The world tries to return

00:11:36.425 --> 00:11:39.553
to its original path.

00:11:40.221 --> 00:11:41.347
It's a theory.

00:11:44.016 --> 00:11:48.103
So you won't die that easily. Relax.

00:11:50.439 --> 00:11:54.109
First, stop taking the E-Capsules.

00:11:55.569 --> 00:11:58.906
I'm healing, and I told Shion
to stop taking them, too.

00:12:01.367 --> 00:12:04.453
So, Yanagi and the others didn't die
from someone's Esper attack,

00:12:04.537 --> 00:12:06.914
but from the side effects
of the E-capsule?

00:12:06.997 --> 00:12:09.833
Yeah. Kizashi admitted it.

00:12:09.917 --> 00:12:14.046
But Kizashi brought the recipe
for the E-capsules and had them made.

00:12:14.129 --> 00:12:16.173
